description: Enferno Storm Commerce API Client library.
releaseNotes:
## What's new?

### OrderService:
- #2657: New, or modified, entities and methods now exist for Invoices. New methods are GetInvoice, GetInvoiceByNo,  ListInvoices and ListInvoicesByBasket. New entities are InvoicePagedList and InvoiceListItem. Invoice and InvoiceItem have been modified slightly.  Invoice.DeliveryMode has changed name to DeliveryMethod.
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/GetInvoiceByNo
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/ListInvoices
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/GetInvoice
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/ListInvoicesByBasket
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoicePagedList
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoiceListItem
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/Invoice
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoiceItem

## What's fixed?

### CustomerService:
- #2798 Company.Pricelists now only gets populated with active company pricelist.

### OrderService:
- #2212: Due to performance problems with OrderList and ListOrders, ListOrder2 they have now been deprecated. There is now a new ListOrders3 with a more light weight resultset, OrderPagedList2 with items as OrderListItem. Basically all references to DeliveryNotes have been removed from list results. The Order entity should be unchanged.
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/ListOrders3
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/OrderListItem

## Miscellaneous changes?

- #2664: We now have an API client for PHP which is located at
https://github.com/StormCommerce/Storm.API-client-php
It can be used by those building solutions using PHP.
